search_results.title: Dj Lazy K - EverybodyWiki Bios & Wiki
search_results.snippet: Dj Lazy K whose real name is Karina Toliver was born on January 12, 1973 in Mexico. She is a producer and disc jockey in the United States.

search_results.title: DJ Lazy K - Age, Family, Bio
search_results.snippet: DJ Lazy K ; About. Mexican-American DJ who is primarily known as an in-demand hip-hop DJ, though she also spins classics from genres ranging from reggae to R&B.
